{"tid":2274293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母蕭若元，講三個州全部畀人反cap","createTime":"2020-11-06T10:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T07:11:03.000Z","uid":43785,"like":23,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0a5f55c7f801e08f2fabe45b3d04de13803cbf","tid":2274293,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"蕭若元：特朗普會在搖擺州份- 喬治亞州 密歇根州 威斯康辛州取勝<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V8qBwQ63o34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV8qBwQ63o34&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9qnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=8735c59b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V8qBwQ63o34</a><br />\n\t由1:40開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪，就係呢三個一個一個咁畀人反cap咗，搞到特朗普輸撚咗成個選舉。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪，明知自己講嘢唔撚掂就算撚數啊，咁撚多口水做乜鳩。<br />\n<br />\n搞撚掂你自己個仔未呀。<br />\n個仔蕭定一響大陸搵食，搵咗咁多年，奶共奶撚到仆街。蕭定一死全家就啱㗎喇<br />\n本身都唔撚想講，間公司都同大陸有千絲萬縷嘅關係。以前話佢人民幣力量嘅時候已經畀人講過好多次。<br />\n<br />\n今次好搞唔搞，搞埋香港人最後希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好想特朗普做多四年呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌<br />\n<br />\n今鋪真係多撚謝燒山。"},{"pid":"d2d549d4a2f826a479dd74c8f096a9748c380678","tid":2274293,"uid":312193,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jxsd8nr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxsd8nr.gif&h=fd3c0fba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0UKuT1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0UKuT1.gif&h=ea5ee1e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WVRM4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WVRM4c.png&h=ec331784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d14575b8cf793e004cf0df5f7237ffac51a027a5","tid":2274293,"uid":49336,"like":2,"d